divs: Sighting Detailswas warming up my car to go somewhere,decided not to go,went outside to turn my car off and noticed the objects.ran inside to get my phone to get a picture came out and only one was left.they appeared to be moving slowly.I felt excited to witness it,but not overwhelmed by it.Have not told anyone about it.
